虽然热巧克力通常作为饮料饮用，但其也可能对健康有正面影响。2003年，[[康奈尔大学|康奈尔大学]]研究发现可可含有大量[[抗氧化剂|抗氧化剂]]，或能帮助抵御癌症。<ref name="anti">{{cite web|url=http://www.news.cornell.edu/releases/Nov03/HotCocoa-Lee.bpf.html|date=2003-12-03|last=Friedlander Jr.|first=Blaine P.|title=Ahhhh! Better than red wine or green tea, cocoa froths with cancer-preventing compounds, Cornell food scientists say|accessdate=2008-07-05|publisher=Cornell News|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080621065430/http://www.news.cornell.edu/releases/Nov03/HotCocoa-Lee.bpf.html|archive-date=2008-06-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>16世纪至19世纪，热巧克力除了充当饮料外也用作药物。<ref name="Rediscover" />

探险家弗朗西斯科·埃尔南德斯（{{lang|en|Francisco Hernández}}）记录道，巧克力饮料能用于治疗发热和肝病。<ref name="Rediscover"/>另一位探险家圣地亚哥·德·巴尔韦尔德·特里希思（{{lang|en|Santiago de Valverde Turices}}）认为，饮用大量热巧克力有助治疗肺部疾病，饮用少量则能治疗胃病。<ref name="Rediscover"/>17世纪，巧克力被引进法国时，报道称其可用于“对抗愤怒和坏脾气”，这种功效可能与巧克力中的[[苯乙胺|苯乙胺]]成分有关。<ref name="Illustrated"/><ref name="ynhh nutrition">{{Cite web|title=Chocolate: Food of the Gods|url=https://www.ynhh.org/services/nutrition/chocolate.aspx|work=Yale New Haven Hospital|accessdate=2020-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713203830/https://www.ynhh.org/services/nutrition/chocolate.aspx|archive-date=2019-07-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>

巧克力最初流行时受到天主教派的抵制。<ref name="ToP">{{Cite book|title=Tastes of paradise: a social history of spices, stimulants, and intoxicants|last=Schivelbusch|first=Wolfgang|publisher=Vintage Books|year=1993|isbn=|location=New York|pages=}}</ref>其为液体饮料，不能用于破斋。<ref name="ToP" />有人认为，[[咖啡|咖啡]]是对身体好但伤害心神的饮料，巧克力则可以滋润人的潜能，所以可以饮用巧克力来恢复咖啡造成的伤害。<ref name="ToP" />

另一方面，由于一些热巧克力饮品含有大量糖<ref name="Health">{{cite web|url=http://www.annamariavolpi.com/chocolate01.html|title=Can Chocolate Benefit Your Health?|last=Bonneville|first=Marguerite|accessdate=2008-06-27|publisher=Open Kitchen|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303170357/http://www.annamariavolpi.com/chocolate01.html|archivedate=2016-03-03}}</ref>、氢化食用油和脂肪<ref name="White">{{cite web|url=http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/woman/health/575585/Health-Trans-fats-Hot-drinks.html|title=Killer fats hidden in hot drinks|last=White|first=Ellie|date=2007-12-13|publisher=News Group Newspapers Ltd|accessdate=2009-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090827013121/http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/woman/health/575585/Health-Trans-fats-Hot-drinks.html|archive-date=2009-08-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>，它也可能对健康造成负面影响。

某些产品广告声称睡前饮用热巧克力有助于睡眠。<ref>Whittard of Chelsea - Whittard of Chelsea Plc - Hot Chocolate {{cite web |url=http://www.whittard.co.uk/ProductDetails.aspx?pid=214148&cid=hc4010&language=en-GB |title=Luxury Hot Chocolate |accessdate=2007-10-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071101110548/http://www.whittard.co.uk/ProductDetails.aspx?pid=214148&cid=hc4010&language=en-GB |archivedate=2007-11-01 }}</ref>但有人认为，巧克力含有[[咖啡因|咖啡因]]，因而不利于睡眠。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://seniorliving.about.com/od/sleep/a/sleep_tips.htm |title=How to Get a Good Night’s Sleep |first=Sharon |last=O'Brien |accessdate=2007-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071013130709/http://seniorliving.about.com/od/sleep/a/sleep_tips.htm |archive-date=2007-10-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>不过其含量较低，一份热巧克力约有10毫克咖啡因，为咖啡的十分之一。<ref name="ynhh nutrition" />

=== 正面影响 ===
[[File:Hot_chocolate_antioxidants_graph-zh.jpg|thumb]]和[[绿茶|绿茶]]中的抗氧化剂含量|alt=一幅图表，展示了热巧克力、红酒和绿茶的抗氧化剂含量。热巧克力最高、红酒其次、绿茶最少。]]
研究表明饮用热巧克力对健康有正面影响。康奈尔大学一项研究显示，热巧克力比红酒、绿茶含有更多的抗氧化剂，能降低心脏疾病的风险。<ref name="daily"/>研究人员发现，一份热巧克力中含有611毫克等量[[没食子酸|没食子酸]]（GAE）和564毫克等量[[儿茶素|儿茶素]]（ECE），而红酒中含有340毫克GAE、163毫克ECE，绿茶则含有165毫克GAE、47毫克ECE。<ref name="anti" />康奈尔大学教授、主导这项研究的研究员{{lang|en|Chang Yong Lee}}表示，巧克力饮料加热时会释放大量抗氧化剂。<ref name="daily" />

制作热巧克力所使用的可可豆含有[[黄酮类化合物|黄酮类化合物]]，其对动脉血管健康有益。一项由[[玛氏食品|玛氏食品]]支持、[[国立卫生研究院_(美国)|美国国立卫生研究院]]进行的研究显示，饮用富含[[黄烷醇|黄烷醇]]的可可饮料后血液流动改善。<ref name="Times">{{cite web |url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9E01E0D8173DF934A25751C0A9629C8B63 |title=Beyond Delicious, Chocolate May Help Pump Up Your Heart |last=Olson |first=Elizabeth |date=2004-02-17 |work=The New York Times |accessdate=2008-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090122134540/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9E01E0D8173DF934A25751C0A9629C8B63 |archive-date=2009-01-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>研究中，实验对象（27名年龄介于18至72岁之间的成人）每天饮用含有900毫克黄烷醇的可可饮料，持续五天，最终发现“血液流动以及血管附近[[内皮细胞|内皮细胞]]的功能显著改善”。<ref name="Times" />此外，也有研究表明，妇女长期摄取富含黄烷醇的可可能减轻紫外线照射带来的红疹并改善皮肤状况。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Long-Term Ingestion of High Flavanol Cocoa Provides Photoprotection against UV-Induced Erythema and Improves Skin Condition in Women|first1=Ulrike|last1=Heinrich|first2=Karin|last2=Neukam|first3=Hagen|last3=Tronnier|first4=Helmut|last4=Sies|first5=Wilhelm|last5=Stahl|url=https://academic.oup.com/jn/article/136/6/1565/4664397#111002051|journal=The Journal of Nutrition|volume=136|issue=6|date=2006-06-01|pages=1565-1569|doi=10.1093/jn/136.6.1565|author=|access-date=2020-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200608174559/https://academic.oup.com/jn/article/136/6/1565/4664397#111002051|archive-date=2020-06-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[布莱根妇女医院|布莱根妇女医院]]及[[哈佛医学院|哈佛医学院]]教授诺曼·K·霍伦伯格（{{lang|en|Norman K. Hollenberg}}）主导的进一步研究发现，黄烷醇有助血管舒张、防止血小板聚集于血管壁。<ref name="Times" />热巧克力中的黄烷醇可以抵御[[自由基|自由基]]对血管壁的伤害，<ref name="Clinic">{{cite web |url=http://my.clevelandclinic.org/heart/prevention/nutrition/chocolate.aspx |title=Your Heart and Vascular Health |date=1995–2008 |publisher=The Cleveland Clinic |accessdate=2008-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080717081502/http://my.clevelandclinic.org/heart/prevention/nutrition/chocolate.aspx |archive-date=2008-07-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>还被认为可以平衡[[类花生酸|类花生酸]]的水平，对心血管健康有正面影响。<ref name="Clinic" />

=== 负面影响 ===
热巧克力也可能对健康有一些负面影响。对于不同种类的热巧克力，其影响类型和程度也不同。<ref name="cocoa vs choc">{{cite web|url=http://bestfriendscocoa.com/cocoa_vs_choc.html|title=Hot Cocoa vs. Hot Chocolate|accessdate=2008-06-29|last=Guttman|first=Linda|author2=Uri Guttman|publisher=Best Friends Cocoa|year=2008|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080531100109/http://www.bestfriendscocoa.com/cocoa_vs_choc.html|archive-date=2008-05-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>使用牛奶制成的热巧克力含有牛奶中的糖类。即食可可粉则通常添加额外的食糖。<ref name="Riches" />一些品牌还含有氢化食用油和脂肪，其中最常见的是椰子油衍生物。<ref name="White"/>这些人工食用油可能提高血液内[[低密度脂蛋白|低密度脂蛋白]]的含量，同时降低[[高密度脂蛋白|高密度脂蛋白]]的含量，进而提高心脏病发生的风险。<ref name="White"/><ref name=ATPIII2003>{{Cite book | author = National Institutes of Health | title = Third Report of the Expert Panel on Detection, Evaluation, and Treatment of High Blood Cholesterol in Adults (Adult Treatment Panel III) Full Report | url = https://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/sites/default/files/publications/02-5215.pdf | year = 2002 | publisher = NIH publication | pages = IV-1-3 | access-date = 2020-06-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200412072158/https://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/sites/default/files/publications/02-5215.pdf | archive-date = 2020-04-12 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

